0.1.name: wordpress/ellipsis-adnet-code-snippet-plugin
0.1.description: ellipsis AdNet is a network of trusted publishers and merchants that enables simple, safe and transparent partnership for the purpose of advertising over the Internet. AdNet cuts the "middle man" and helps connect publishers and merchants with full transparency. This plugin will help you embed ellipsis AdNet Banner, Text and Lead Capture Ads within your blog posts.
